          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Targets of UO(2) were prepared by multiple thermal",
                "decomposition of uranium nitrate cellulose painted on",
                "10- and 100-mumeters thick Al-backing.  The average",
                "thickness of the U-236 layer was about 100-mug/cm**2.",
                "The thickness variations were within 3%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".The results are discussed and compared with",
                "previous data on the other reactions yielding the same",
                "final products."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TTY-C"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".The calculated thick-target yields of Pu-236,",
                " Pu-237, Pu-238 and Np-235."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "2SF JYV"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The K-130 cyclotron of the University",
                " of Jyvaskyla."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The beam current was approximately 3 muA at",
                "41-MeV and 0.5 muA at 60-MeV He3 beam."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Irradiation time, 4 hours at 41-MeV and",
                "20-hours at 60-MeV."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " In each irradiation six U-236 targets and",
                "energy-degrading Al-foils of different thickness were",
                "mounted in a multiple target system on two water-cooled",
                "Al-plates.  The He-3 ion energy at each target was",
                "calculated from the range-energy relation-ships in Al",
                "and in the target materials."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
